        "jsdocRaw": "/**\n * @auto-doc\n * @title Docs Detail Page Emitter\n * @group Output\n * Produces generated UI source for `/docs/[slug]/+page.svelte`.\n * @returns Svelte source for docs detail with author card and contrast-safe light mode.\n */",
